ts=2026-02-24T16:57:17.791Z type=context scope=decoright content="DecoRight is a service-request platform for a local Algerian decoration & interior design company. Production phase. Deployed at https://decoright.netlify.app via Netlify. Main branch auto-deploys. Dev branch is for development work." tags=project,overview,deployment
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:22.729Z type=context scope=decoright/stack content="Stack: React 19 + TypeScript 5.9, Vite 7, Tailwind CSS 4, Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Realtime + Storage), i18next (EN/AR/FR), pnpm. Package manager is pnpm." tags=stack,tech,dependencies
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:27.878Z type=context scope=decoright/roles content="Three user roles: Guest (unauthenticated, limited access), Customer (authenticated, can submit requests and chat), Admin (full access, manages requests via Kanban, manages portfolio/gallery/FAQs). Services offered: Interior Design, Fixed Design, Decor Consultation. No pricing logic — all pricing via chat." tags=roles,business-logic
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:31.847Z type=context scope=decoright/requests content="Service request lifecycle: Submitted → Under Review → Waiting for Client Info → Approved → In Progress → Completed (or Rejected). Status changes are admin-only." tags=service-requests,lifecycle,status
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:36.498Z type=context scope=decoright/database content="DB tables (public schema, all RLS-enabled): profiles, service_requests, messages, chat_rooms, projects, project_images, gallery_items, likes, testimonials, service_types, space_types, request_attachments, contact_messages, faqs, site_settings, admin_activities." tags=database,schema,tables
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:42.479Z type=pattern scope=decoright/conventions content="Code conventions: PascalCase for components/types/interfaces, camelCase for variables/functions/hooks, UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for constants. Prefix hooks with 'use', suffix service objects with 'Service'. Path aliases: @/ for src root, @components/ for components. Import order: React → Libraries → Aliases → Relative. Use 'type' keyword for type-only imports. Throw errors in services, catch in components with toast notifications (react-hot-toast)." tags=code-style,conventions,naming
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:47.035Z type=context scope=decoright/git content="Git: dev branch for all development work, main auto-deploys to Netlify. Conventional commits format: feat/fix/refactor(scope): message. Collaborator (friend) also pushes to remote dev branch." tags=git,workflow,branches
ts=2026-02-24T16:57:52.138Z type=context scope=decoright/architecture content="Key services: src/services/request.service.ts (CRUD for requests), src/services/chat.service.ts (messages, file uploads), src/services/portfolio.service.ts (projects, gallery). Storage bucket: request-attachments. Auth: Supabase email OTP, role in profiles.role ('customer' | 'admin'). Route protection via RequireAuth.tsx and RequireRole.tsx." tags=architecture,services,auth,routing
